name: 3iQ Solana Staking ETF
longDescription: To achieve its investment objectives, the 3iQ Solana Staking ETF will invest in long-term  holdings  of  SOL,  purchased  from  reputable  digital  asset  trading  platforms  and  OTC  counterparties, in order to provide investors with a convenient, safer alternative to a direct  investment in SOL. The 3iQ Solana Staking ETFs investment objectives are to seek to provide holders of Units  (Unitholders) of the 3iQ Solana Staking ETF with (a) exposure to the digital asset Solana (SOL) and the daily price movements of the U.S. dollar price of SOL, and (b) the opportunity  for longterm capital appreciation.
